Kim "Forte" Ki Yong, previously known as SalvatioN, is a retired Terran StarCraft II player from South Korea.

Wings of Liberty [ edit ]

2012 [ edit ]

On March 11, in the 2012 Global StarCraft II League Season 1 Preliminaries SalvatioN has made it to the Quarterfinals of the Group 6 where he lost 2-1
